name: Start[001] Hotsite Builder
description:
This is our first **decentralized startup template builder** (fully responsive), built on **Ethereum**, **Javascript**, **HTML5**, **CSS3**, **jQuery** and **Bootstrap**.

The builder is **stored in your wallet** and managed only by you. **Build hundreds of decentralized websites with just one builder**.

It is in the process of finalizing development and the whitelist is not yet defined.'
